<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="65 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">雖然現在這裡看不到，<delay20 />
不過以前我住的地方，<delay8 />星期一晚上<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會播我最喜歡的電視節目喔。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />介紹《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》<delay8 />
這本書的那集，<delay8 />真是太精彩了。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為節目介紹得很有趣又很搞笑，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看得超過癮的啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我最後<delay20 />還是沒去看那本書，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />節目裡有個偶像表演幽默短劇的單元，<delay20 />
搞笑功力簡直比專業搞笑藝人還厲害<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到這麼拼命努力的人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也會忍不住想替對方加油啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是看了這個節目才知道，<delay20 />
原來大阪燒翻面時用的工具，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然有那麼多種稱呼！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是平鏟、<delay20 />大阪燒鏟、<delay20 />鐵板燒鏟等等<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自從看了那個節目，<delay8 />
我好像也變得比較聰明了耶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="66 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我最近<delay8 />總是做些奇怪的夢耶<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="102_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">像是在夢裡一腳踩空，<delay20 />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嚇了一跳！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />然後我就驚醒了……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />夢到這種事，<delay8 />誰都會嚇到吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />一邊面帶微笑，<delay8 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一邊飛快地朝我追過來，<delay8 />
這樣的夢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我沒想到<gender3 m="他" f="她" />竟然可以跑得那麼快<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還真是不容小覷啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是夢裡的<tag a="110" b="33" />，<delay20 />
就和我知道的樣子有些不一樣，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />紅色的天空看起來特別詭異<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />是叫什麼來著啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
好像叫<delay20 />「平巡世界」吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay8 />我記錯了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="67 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，<delay8 />今天是星期三呢。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="103_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">以前每到星期三，學校都會比較早放學。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我回家都會直接把背包扔在玄關，<delay20 />
然後馬上跑出去玩！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得一到星期三，<delay20 />
就特別容易回憶起小時候的事耶。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道<delay20 />媽媽最近過得好不好？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到星期三，<delay20 />我小時候<delay8 />
總是得陪媽媽去買東西～<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還記得<delay8 />我們為了買一人限購一盒的特價雞蛋，<delay20 />
當時排隊排了好久呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="68 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是星期四啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我以前住在其他地方的時候，<delay8 />
星期四晚上都會準時收看一個電視節目呢。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="104_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「跟拍！<tag a="135" b="5" arg="0xcd00" />迷的一日生活！」<delay frames="30" />
我記得<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個節目真的非常有趣！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能更了解以前沒接觸過的世界喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個節目會請很多
<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />的高手進行比賽，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人看著都跟著熱血沸騰了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個節目會請偶像來朗讀<delay8 />
《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》，<delay8 /><delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過實在不怎麼有趣就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="69 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />星期五一下就到了耶。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="105_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在每週五都會開一個
「<tag a="110" b="10" />自我反省會」喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你問我在反省什麼？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個世界上有些事情，<delay8 />
還是不要知道比較好喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />我們這個星期好好全力衝刺了呢～<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太棒啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個週末也要繼續保持這股衝勁！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">話說回來啊，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我爸常說什麼「週五狂歡日」<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過又說<delay8 />這並不是指星期五<delay8 />
一定要在外面狂歡！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />這很容易讓人搞混耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="6a 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">已經到週末了啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得一個星期<delay8 />一眨眼就過了！</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="106_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以前每到週六晚上，<delay20 />
我都會和死黨們聚會呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真讓人懷念啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還小的時候，<delay20 />
每到星期六晚上，<delay8 />就會玩得特別起勁～<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明爸媽也都在熬夜，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />卻總是叫小孩子<delay20 /><anim id="Outraged" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「早點去睡覺」！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真沒道理……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我這個星期<delay20 />做了什麼啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />算了，<delay20 />這種小事不重要！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要今天過得好，<delay8 />整個星期都會很好啦。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="6b 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎唷！<delay20 />今天是週日啦！</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="107_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看起來挺享受今天的樣子啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />不賴嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />星期日的時候啊，<delay20 />一個不小心<delay8 />
就會穿著運動服度過一整天呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們彼此多注意一下吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="3" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我們一起拋開煩惱，<delay8 />盡情狂歡吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>